NUMBER 2330
NAME Living Area
REGION 0
CHANNEL 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT

*DESCRIPTION_START
The main rooms of this simple but elegant home share the front of the house
without walls between them, giving an open, spacious feeling. Conveniently
placed next to the tidy kitchen is a long dining room table surrounded by
high-backed chairs. The other side of the room features a large, comfortable
sofa and easy chair facing a coffee table in front of the brick fireplace and
fur rug. Bookshelves holding tomes and tools for healing, alchemy and
psionics line the richly appointed study to the left of the fireplace, while
a sewing area fills the corner to the right of the fireplace.
*DESCRIPTION_END

