*DESCRIPTION_START
Flowerbeds with violets and budding rose bushes grow by the side of the road
surrounding a newly remodeled house. Lush grape vines twine up the side of a
quaint gazebo, visible through its arch just to the north. A small stand with
a sign displays the price of the flowers in season.
*DESCRIPTION_END

