EXITO 2331

*DESCRIPTION_START
Large hanging pots containing lush plants grace the ceiling of the gazebo.
Their foliage cascades down, displaying groups of brightly colored, tubular
flowers. A heady perfume fills the air. An iron chair sits on the ground,
overgrown by vines.
*DESCRIPTION_END
